            <title>[HBASE-14899] Create custom Streaming ReplicationEndpoint</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-14899</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Create a custom Replication Endpoint that streams WALEntry directly through client API.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
